1. create a variable named "author" and its value is your full name.
2. Use "yum" module to finish the TASK <install nginx>  
3. In TASK <update web page>, use "template" module to copy index.html.j2 to /usr/share/nginx/html/index.html
4. In index.html.j2, replace <This instance's FQDN> with an appropriate variable from ansible facts.
5. Also in index.html.j2, replace <YOUR NAME> with the variable "author"
